  "prompt": "A good friend of mine is gay , but we made out before telling me. Is there any chance he is bisexual ?",
  "response": "There is a possibility that your friend could be bisexual. Sexual orientation can be complex, and people might identify differently based on their attractions to different genders. It's also possible that he was exploring his feelings or experiencing a moment of attraction. The best way to understand his orientation is to have an open and honest conversation with him. Ask him how he identifies and how he feels about the situation, offering support and understanding regardless of his response. Respecting his perspective and being open to his experiences will help maintain a healthy and supportive friendship.",
